# GIAI ĐOẠN 3: MẪU KIẾN TRÚC BẮT BUỘC (Non-Negotiable Patterns)

## 3.1 Data-Driven

```
✅ DÙNG: ScriptableObject cho all static data
   CardData, PackData, RarityDefinition, FurnitureDefinition

❌ CẤM: Giá trị gameplay hardcoded trong MonoBehaviour
```

## 3.2 Event-Driven Communication

```
✅ DÙNG: Delegate/Event pattern cho cross-system communication
   CustomerFSM → CharacterMovement events
   PathfindingGrid → OnGridChanged
   PlacementManager → OnFurniturePlaced

❌ CẤM: GameObject.Find(), GetComponent() trong Update()
❌ CẤM: Direct reference giữa unrelated systems
```

## 3.3 O(1) Lookups

```
✅ DÙNG: Dictionary<Vector2Int, GridNode> cho grid
✅ DÙNG: Dictionary<string, PackData> cho card lookup
✅ DÙNG: Dictionary<string, int> cho inventory

❌ CẤM: List.Find() cho runtime lookups trong gameplay
```

## 3.4 Graceful Fallbacks

```
✅ BẮT BUỘC: Mọi lỗi phải có:
  1. Debug.LogError với context cực kỳ cụ thể
  2. Fallback action để game tiếp tục chạy
  3. KHÔNG BAO GIỜ để NPC đứng im (freeze)

VÍ DỤ ĐÚNG:
  Debug.LogError($"[CustomerFSM - {InstanceId}] PathNotFound to Shelf_02 at {targetCell}. " +
                "Triggering Fallback to ExitShop.");
  TransitionToState(CustomerState.ExitShop);

VÍ DỤ SAI:
  Debug.LogWarning("Path not found."); // Không có context!
  return; // Silent fail — NPC đứng im!
```

## 3.5 Isometric Rendering

```
✅ BẮT BUỘC:
  - TransparencySortMode = Custom Axis
  - TransparencySortAxis = (0, 1, -0.26)
  - Pivot = Bottom Center cho tất cả sprites
  - SortingOrder = round(worldY × -100) + offset
```

## 3.6 Input System

```
✅ BẮT BUỘC: Unity New Input System cho mọi input
  - Mouse.current cho desktop
  - Touch.activeTouches cho mobile
  - Keyboard.current cho keyboard shortcuts

❌ CẤM: Input.GetKey, Input.GetMouseButton (old Input system)
```

## 3.7 Logging Standards

```
✅ FORMAT BẮT BUỘC:
  [ClassName] {InstanceId hoặc context cụ thể}: {action} {result}

VÍ DỤ:
  [CustomerFSM - customer_0042_1715001234] PathNotFound in state SeekingShelf. 
    Target: Shelf_02 at Vector2Int(5,5). Triggering Fallback to ExitShop.

  [PathfindingCore] Start cell (3,3) → Goal cell (5,5). 
    Path found: 4 steps. Time: 0.12ms.

❌ SAI:
  Debug.Log("Path not found");           // Không có class name!
  Debug.LogWarning("Error");              // Không có context!
```

