# GIAI ĐOẠN 4: THUẬT TOÁN BẮT BUỘC

## 4.1 Gacha RNG — Cumulative Weighted Probability

```
CÔNG THỨC:
  1. Tính totalWeight = tổng tất cả weights trong slot
  2. Roll = Random.Range(0f, totalWeight)
  3. Duyệt cumulative: roll < cumulativeWeight → chọn rarity

KHÔNG DÙNG: Random.value < rarityPercent (normalize thủ công)
PHẢI DÙNG: Cumulative weighted probability như trên
```

## 4.2 Economic Decision

```
priceRatio = sellPrice / marketPrice

IF priceRatio <= 1.0:
    probability = 0.95

ELSE:
    steps = FLOOR((priceRatio - 1.0) × 100 / 5)
    probability = MAX(0.95 - steps × 0.15, 0.0)

QUYẾT ĐỊNH:
  probability == 0.0 → AbsoluteRefusal → Angry bubble
  probability < 0.40  → NormalRefusal  → Neutral bubble
  probability >= 0.40 → HappyPurchase  → Heart bubble
```

## 4.3 A* Pathfinding

```
HEURISTIC: Manhattan Distance (|dx| + |dy|) × 10
OPEN LIST: MinHeap<PathNode> (O(log n))
CLOSED SET: HashSet<PathNode> (O(1))
DIAGONAL: Disabled (4-directional only)
```

