# GIAI ĐOẠN 5: CẤU TRÚC THƯ MỤC

```
src/TCGShopSimulator/Assets/
├── Scripts/
│   ├── Camera/          # CameraController
│   ├── Character/       # CharacterMovement
│   ├── Core/            # GameManager, SceneBootstrapper
│   ├── Customer/        # CustomerFSM, CustomerSpawner, EconomicDecisionEngine
│   ├── Data/            # All ScriptableObjects
│   ├── Debug/           # Debug testers (NOT in production build)
│   ├── Editor/          # Custom inspectors (Editor only)
│   ├── Gacha/          # GachaEngine, GachaResult
│   ├── Grid/            # GridSystem, GridNode, GridVisualizer
│   ├── Inventory/       # InventoryManager, InventoryEntry
│   ├── Pathfinding/     # PathfindingCore, PathfindingGrid, PathNode, MinHeap
│   ├── Placement/       # PlacementManager, GhostObject, PlacedFurnitureInstance
│   ├── Shop/            # ShopFloorManager, ShelfInstance, CashierQueueManager
│   ├── UI/              # SpeechBubble, future UI
│   └── World/           # IsometricSortingController
└── Scenes/
    └── GameScene.unity

src/_AIDocs/              # AI LIVING DOCUMENTATION (đọc TRƯỚC KHI code)
├── 01_Project_Status.md  # Trạng thái dự án
├── 02_Architecture_Map.md # Sơ đồ luồng dữ liệu
├── 03_Data_Structures.md # Tất cả data structures
└── (tương lai: 04_Open_Questions.md, 05_Changelog.md)
```

