# GIAI ĐOẠN 6: OPEN/CLOSED PRINCIPLE

## 6.1 Mở rộng cho Staff AI

```csharp
// ✅ ĐÚNG: Staff AI mở rộng từ EntityBase interface
public interface IAgent
{
    string AgentId { get; }
    float EvaluatePriority();
    void ExecuteAction();
}

public abstract class EntityBase : MonoBehaviour
{
    protected CharacterMovement Movement;
    protected IAgent Agent;
}

// CustomerFSM : EntityBase → sử dụng existing CharacterMovement
// StaffAI : EntityBase     → reuse CharacterMovement, override IAgent
```

## 6.2 Mở rộng cho Play Tables

```csharp
// ✅ ĐÚNG: PlayTable mở rộng từ IInteractable
public interface IInteractable
{
    bool CanInteract(CharacterBase agent);
    void Interact(CharacterBase agent);
}

public class ShelfInstance : MonoBehaviour, IInteractable { /* existing */ }
public class PlayTableInstance : MonoBehaviour, IInteractable { /* NEW */ }
```

